1. Checks each row to ensure it contains all digits 1-9 exactly once
2. Checks each column (using zip(*board)) for the same condition
3. Checks each 3x3 sub-grid by iterating through the 9 sub-grids
4. Returns True only if all three conditions are satisfied for the entire board

